REL-1: .github/workflows/ci.yml — build, test, lint (dotnet format), gitleaks secret scan, CodeQL, single 'CI Gate' required check.
REL-2: .github/workflows/deploy-staging.yml — OIDC azd deploy on push to main, Playwright smoke, auto-rollback on smoke failure via Container Apps revision pinning.
REL-3: .github/CODEOWNERS routes booking/payments/auth paths and PR template enforces tests + security checklist + reviewer routing.
REL-4: docs/feature-flags.md — Azure App Configuration conventions, required day-1 flags incl. ops.deploy.killSwitch.
REL-5: docs/runbooks/rollback.md — < 5 min rollback procedure with automatic, one-command, manual, and kill-switch options.

Co-authored-by: Copilot <223556219+Copilot@users.noreply.github.com>
